text: Nikol Švantnerová (born 21 October 1992) is a Czech model and beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Česká Miss 2015 and represented the Czech Republic at Miss Universe 2015. ==Personal life== Švantnerová was born in Šumperk, but has lived in České Budějovice most of her life. She was a student and completed her degree. In her spare time, she loves watching sports, especially football, with her family and friends. She is also fascinated with foreign languages and had intentions to learn French and Spanish. ===Česká Miss 2015=== Švantnerová was crowned Česká Miss 2015 and represented Šumperk at the pageant on 28 March 2015. The pageant aired live on FTV Prima. ===Miss Universe 2015=== Švantnerová competed at the Miss Universe 2015 pageant but did not place. ==References== ==External links== *Ceska Miss official website Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Czech beauty pageant winners Category:Miss Universe 2015 contestants Category:People from Šumperk Category:Czech female models Category:Footballers' wives and girlfriends
